posting_body: ['Marbrisa Apartments', '1809 Termino Ave.', 'Long Beach, CA. 90815', 'show contact info', 'https://essexapts.info/Marbrisa', 'Every home reflects your personality, and we want to help you find the perfect fit!', 'Whether you’re moving in with a four-legged friend, looking for a space to accommodate your family, or searching for an ideal place to call your own, we have a home for you.', 'The apartment of your dreams is waiting for you at Marbrisa Apartments.', 'Our scenic apartment community is located right in the heart of Long Beach, just a few miles away from the shores of the Pacific.', 'And, with our winter incentives, the time has never been better to make your move.', 'Lease your new one bedroom apartment home at just $2661 per month on a 12 month lease term!', 'Now offering flexible lease terms.', 'Prices may vary.', 'Copy and Paste this link for a 3D VIRTUAL TOUR: <URL>', 'We are also offering Self Guided Tours!', 'Call us for details!', 'For more information please visit our website: https://essexapts.info/Marbrisa', '-Large Patio', '-Assigned Parking Space', '-Dishwasher', '-Ceaserstone Counter tops', '-Resident Events', '-Central Air and Heat', '-Stainless Steel Appliances', '-Stack-able Washer and Dryer', '-Package Acceptance', '-Professional Onsite Management available 6 days a week', '-30-Day Satisfaction Guarantee', 'We offer a 30-day satisfaction guarantee with any leased apartment.', 'If you’re not 100% satisfied with your new home, we’ll help you transfer to a comparable home within the same community or you can choose to terminate your lease.*', 'Equal Housing Opportunity', '**All Pricing and Availability is Subject to Change**', 'Do NOT contact me with unsolicited services or offers']
